metadata.name: Overseer Beyond Planet Earth
metadata.description:
This piece is my first step in building a world with the use of one of my cyborg the "Overseer" an intelligent being. After decades of service monitoring anomalies on the surface of planet Earth for it's creators and masters. It decides to leave the atmosphere and  explore freely what the cosmos has to offer in order to fulfil it's desire of discovery and knowledge.
.
3Dpiece hand model with paint over: 3500x4600 PX
